        <span class="lp-cat-name">Moda e Acessórios</span>
        <span class="lp-cat-count">54 produtos</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SPLIT CÃO vs GATO -->
<div class="lp-split">
  <div class="lp-container lp-split-inner">
    <a href="/collections/caes" class="lp-split-card lp-split-dog">
      <div class="lp-split-deco">
        <svg width="72" height="72" viewBox="0 0 72 72" fill="none"><ellipse cx="36" cy="44" rx="20" ry="14" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5"/><circle cx="26" cy="28" r="8" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5"/><circle cx="46" cy="28" r="8" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5"/><path d="M18 24c-3-5-8-6-11-4" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M54 24c3-5 8-6 11-4" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><ellipse cx="27" cy="28" rx="3" ry="3.5" fill="white"/><ellipse cx="45" cy="28" rx="3" ry="3.5" fill="white"/><path d="M30 36c0 0 3 3 6 3s6-3 6-3" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-split-content">
        <h3>Para Cães</h3>
        <p>Coleiras, trelas, camas, brinquedos e muito mais para o teu melhor amigo.</p>
        <span class="lp-split-btn">Ver produtos para cão →</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/collections/gatos" class="lp-split-card lp-split-cat">
      <div class="lp-split-deco">
        <svg width="72" height="72" viewBox="0 0 72 72" fill="none"><path d="M18 16L12 28h10c0 6 6 12 14 12s14-6 14-12h10L54 16l-8 8c-3-3-7-5-10-5s-7 2-10 5L18 16z" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/><ellipse cx="30" cy="30" rx="3" ry="3.5" fill="white"/><ellipse cx="42" cy="30" rx="3" ry="3.5" fill="white"/><path d="M31 36c0 0 2.5 3 5 3s5-3 5-3" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M36 40v8M30 48h12" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-split-content">
        <h3>Para Gatos</h3>
        <p>Arranhadores, bebedouros, brinquedos e tudo o que o teu gato ama.</p>
        <span class="lp-split-btn">Ver produtos para gato →</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PORQUÊ LUX PET -->
<div class="lp-why">
  <div class="lp-container">
    <div class="lp-why-grid">
      <div class="lp-why-text">
        <span class="lp-why-tag">Porquê a Lux Pet?</span>
        <h2>Pensamos no teu animal como se fosse o nosso.</h2>
        <p>Selecionamos cada produto com critério. Só o melhor chega até ti.</p>
        <ul class="lp-why-list">
          <li><span class="lp-why-check"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2 2.5L8 2.5" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>Produtos testados antes de chegarem à loja</li>
          <li><span class="lp-why-check"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2 2.5L8 2.5" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>Entrega em 3–5 dias em Portugal e Espanha</li>
          <li><span class="lp-why-check"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2 2.5L8 2.5" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>Suporte em português, resposta em 24h</li>
          <li><span class="lp-why-check"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none"><path d="M2 5l2 2.5L8 2.5" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>Devolução gratuita em 30 dias</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/collections/all" class="lp-why-cta">Explorar a loja</a>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-why-stats">
        <div class="lp-stat"><span class="lp-stat-num">500+</span><span class="lp-stat-lbl">Produtos disponíveis</span></div>
        <div class="lp-stat"><span class="lp-stat-num">3–5</span><span class="lp-stat-lbl">Dias de entrega</span></div>
        <div class="lp-stat"><span class="lp-stat-num">30</span><span class="lp-stat-lbl">Dias de devolução</span></div>
        <div class="lp-stat"><span class="lp-stat-num">⭐4.9</span><span class="lp-stat-lbl">Avaliação média</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.lp-container{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}

.lp-trust-bar{background:#fff;border-top:1px solid #E4E4E0;border-bottom:1px solid #E4E4E0;padding:4px 0}
.lp-trust-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}
.lp-trust-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:16px 20px;border-right:1px solid #E4E4E0}
.lp-trust-item:last-child{border-right:none}
.lp-trust-ico{width:40px;height:40px;background:#EAF1EC;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
.lp-trust-txt strong{display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1A1A}
.lp-trust-txt span{font-size:12px;color:#6B6B6B}

.lp-cats{padding:56px 0 48px;background:#F7F7F5}
.lp-sec-head{display:flex;align-items:baseline;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:24px}
.lp-sec-title{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1A1A;font-family:Georgia,serif;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.lp-sec-link{font-size:12px;color:#4A7C59;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none}
.lp-cat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:12px}
.lp-cat-card{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;background:#fff;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #E4E4E0;padding:24px 12px 18px;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.2s;gap:8px}
.lp-cat-card:hover{border-color:#4A7C59;background:#EAF1EC;transform:translateY(-2px)}
.lp-cat-ico{width:56px;height:56px;background:#F7F7F5;border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.lp-cat-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1A1A;text-align:center;line-height:1.3}
.lp-cat-count{font-size:11px;color:#9E9E9E}

.lp-split{padding:0 0 48px;background:#F7F7F5}
.lp-split-inner{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px}
.lp-split-card{border-radius:16px;padding:36px 32px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.22s}
.lp-split-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px)}
.lp-split-dog{background:#4A7C59}
.lp-split-cat{background:#2C5F6E}
.lp-split-deco{flex-shrink:0;opacity:0.9}
.lp-split-content h3{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;font-family:Georgia,serif;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.lp-split-content p{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.78);margin-bottom:18px;line-height:1.55}
.lp-split-btn{display:inline-block;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.18);color:#fff;padding:9px 18px;border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;transition:background 0.2s}
.lp-split-card:hover .lp-split-btn{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.28)}

.lp-why{background:#EAF1EC;padding:72px 0}
.lp-why-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr 0.8fr;gap:72px;align-items:center}
.lp-why-tag{display:inline-block;background:#4A7C59;color:#fff;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:5px 14px;border-radius:100px;margin-bottom:18px}
.lp-why-text h2{font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1A1A;font-family:Georgia,serif;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:14px}
.lp-why-text>p{font-size:15px;color:#6B6B6B;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:24px}
.lp-why-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;margin-bottom:32px}
.lp-why-list li{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:14px;color:#1A1A1A}
.lp-why-check{width:20px;height:20px;background:#4A7C59;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
.lp-why-cta{display:inline-block;background:#4A7C59;color:#fff;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;transition:background 0.2s,transform 0.2s}
.lp-why-cta:hover{background:#3A6147;transform:translateY(-1px)}
.lp-why-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px}
.lp-stat{background:#fff;border-radius:14px;padding:28px 20px;text-align:center;border:1px solid #d4e8da}
.lp-stat-num{display:block;font-size:32px;font-weight:700;color:#4A7C59;font-family:Georgia,serif;margin-bottom:6px}
.lp-stat-lbl{font-size:12px;color:#6B6B6B}

@media(max-width:768px){
  .lp-trust-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .lp-trust-item{border-right:none;border-bottom:1px solid #E4E4E0}
  .lp-trust-item:nth-child(odd){border-right:1px solid #E4E4E0}
  .lp-cat-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
  .lp-split-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .lp-why-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}
  .lp-why-stats{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Lux Pet Homepage",
  "tag": "div",
  "class": "lux-pet-homepage",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{"name": "Lux Pet Homepage"}]
}
{% endschema %}
